  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  


Here's my suggestion...

Light Maps.(not bright maps)...
   The ability to use a brushmap to mask off a lightsource
   (without ray-tracing). Would be similar to putting a transparency
   map on a sphere and putting a light in to sphere and tracing, but
   without the sphere and in scanline also.
