@node IML-7 " MSG-7  Subject: Fog scene
@toc contents

Subject: Fog scene
Date:    Saturday, 01 October 1994 20:02:08 
From:    PEDER NAALSUND <PEDNAA@CALVIN.NHIDH.NKI.NO>


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  


Hi folks!

Can anybody help me with Global Fog!
I can make fog objects, but not Global fog.(in Action editor).
