@node IML-77 " MSG-77  Subject: 3.0 -> 3.1 -> 4.0?
@toc contents

Subject: 3.0 -> 3.1 -> 4.0?
Date:    Wednesday, 05 October 1994 03:18:53 
From:    CHIRON1@delphi.com


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  


Hi all!
 
Well, this may be common knowledge, but I don't think that I've read it before.
If this is old news to you, then I apologize.
 
I called Impulse regarding the policy of upgrading from 3.0 to 3.1 and was
informed that upgrading was *ONLY* available through the "Maintenance Upgrade
