And if you don't...

Show your color bars picture.

Turn down Color, Brightness, contrast.

Turn up brightness,untill you slightly see every bar, but when the black bar
starts to turn grey, turn it back down a bit.

Turn up contrast, and get good white and black. The other colors will
 
be grey.

Now turn up the colors, dont let them bleed. Watch for the Blue, Red, Green.

Its not a pro metode. Its for 'simple' people. do it with your TV as well.

